OL,6,FFamilies shared their experiences of
OL,7,Flosing relatives who were admitted to
OL,8,Fhospital for something else and while
OL,9,Fthere caught and died of Covid.
OL,11,FA number of people detailed how their
OL,12,Floved one died of cancer because they
OL,13,Fwere not seen in time due to the
OL,14,Fbacklog in appointments caused by the
OL,15,Fpandemic.
OL,17,FFamilies also said they had struggled
OL,18,Fto see their relatives in hospital
OL,19,Fwith such tight restrictions on
OL,20,Fvisiting.
