OL,6,FTom Poole KC set out the inquiry's
OL,7,Fpurpose, explaining that it will look
OL,8,Fat Welsh Government decision-making
OL,9,Fbetween January 2020 and May 2022.
OL,11,FHe said: "We will enquire into, probe
OL,12,Fand challenge core decisions to see if
OL,13,Fthey were made on the best
OL,14,Finformation, after proper
OL,15,Fconsultation, as part of a well
OL,16,Fordered process and without undue
OL,17,Fdelay or unnecessary prevarication.
