OL,6,FThe second day of the inquiry's time
OL,7,Fin Wales coincides with the four year
OL,8,Fanniversary of the first Covid case
OL,9,Fbeing confirmed in Wales.
OL,11,FIt's the first time decisions will be
OL,12,Fscrutinised in detail.
OL,14,FBaroness Hallett, chair of the
OL,15,FInquiry, will start "substantive
OL,16,Fpublic hearings" into decisions made
OL,17,Fby the Welsh Government and Welsh
OL,18,Fmedical officials during the Covid
OL,19,Fpandemic from March 2020 onwards.
