OL,6,FPlaid Cymru's Health and Social
OL,7,Fspokesperson Mabon ap Gwynfor MS said
OL,8,Fthe UK wide enquiry "will not have the
OL,9,Ftime nor capacity to fully scrutinise
OL,10,Fall decisions made in Wales".
OL,12,F"The Labour Welsh Government's
OL,13,Foutright refusal to establish a Welsh-
OL,14,Fspecific inquiry is a fundamental
OL,15,Fdereliction of accountability and
OL,16,Fundermines devolution. It is
OL,17,Finexcusable."
