OL,6,FAndrew RT Davies, leader of the Welsh
OL,7,FConservatives, has also criticised
OL,8,FWelsh Labour's decision not to have a
OL,9,FWales-specific Covid inquiry. He said:
OL,10,F"The next few weeks will be a reminder
OL,11,Fto those who lost loved ones of how
OL,12,FLabour has robbed them of the answers
OL,13,Fthey deserve.
OL,15,F"While the UK inquiry will doubtless
OL,16,Fdo important work, it cannot give
OL,17,FLabour's decisions the same intricate
OL,18,Fscrutiny as a Wales-specific inquiry
OL,19,Fwould be able to.
