OL,6,F"The Welsh Conservatives believe that
OL,7,Fpeople who lost loved ones deserve a
OL,8,FWales-specific inquiry so they can get
OL,9,Fthe answers they deserve, and that
OL,10,FWales deserves."
OL,12,FThe Welsh Government came to an
OL,13,Fagreement with the Conservatives to
OL,14,Festablish a "Special Purposes"
OL,15,FCommittee tasked with reviewing the
OL,16,Freports from the UK Inquiry, carrying
OL,17,Fout additional investigations into any
OL,18,Fperceived gaps. But Plaid Cymru
OL,19,Frepresentatives have criticised this
OL,20,Fmove, calling it a "back-room deal".
